Canada Sept. Small Business Barometer: Summary

-- B y   A l e x   T a n z i
-- 
2011-10-05T11:32:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/canada-sept-small-business-barometer-summary-table-.html
Canada’s small and mid-size businesses, 
which account for the majority of the nation’s businesses, were more 
optimistic in the Sept. compared to the previous month, according
to a monthly industry survey.  The Canadian Federation of  Independent Business  barometer
index rose to 62.7 in Sept. from 61.7 in the previous month.  Following is a table compiled from the CFIB business 
